devdoc.details: A secure fund management smart contract that allows an owner to deposit and withdraw funds with proper access control and error handling

constructor.details: Constructor sets the contract deployer as the owner

deposit().details: Allows anyone to deposit funds into the contract

getContractBalance().details: Returns the actual contract balance (including any direct transfers)

returns._0: The actual contract balance in wei

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new owner

params.newOwner: The address of the new owner

withdraw(uint256).details: Allows the owner to withdraw funds from the contract

params.amount: The amount to withdraw in wei

returns.error: Error enum indicating the result of the withdrawal
